## Module Descriptions

### CLI Entry Point

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/bin/ff-terminal.ts` | Main CLI router, parses commands, delegates to appropriate handler |

### Terminal UI (Ink)

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/cli/app.tsx` | Main Ink React interface, WebSocket client, state management |
| `src/cli/tts/tts.ts` | Text-to-speech integration |
| `src/cli/tts/audio-player.tsx` | Audio playback queue management |
| `src/cli/components/` | Reusable React components for terminal UI |

### AI Daemon

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/daemon/daemon.ts` | WebSocket server, handles client connections |
| `src/daemon/protocol.ts` | Message type definitions |
| `src/daemon/ws-handler.ts` | WebSocket message handling |

### Runtime Core

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/agentLoop.ts` | Multi-turn conversation loop (max 500 turns) |
| `src/runtime/config/config.ts` | Main configuration loading |
| `src/runtime/config/mounts.ts` | Mount configuration management |
| `src/runtime/profiles/storage.ts` | Profile persistence to filesystem |
| `src/runtime/profiles/credentials.ts` | OS keychain credential storage |

### Tool System

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/tools/registry.ts` | Tool registry and discovery |
| `src/runtime/tools/toolSchemas.ts` | OpenAI-style tool schema definitions |
| `src/runtime/tools/executeTools.ts` | Tool execution orchestration |
| `src/runtime/tools/implementations/` | Individual tool implementations |

### Tool Implementations

| Category | Tools |
|----------|-------|
| **File Operations** | readFile, writeFile, editFile, multiEditFile |
| **Search** | grep, glob, searchCode, astGrep |
| **Execution** | runCommand, subagentTool, agentsWorkflow, commandsWorkflow, skillsWorkflow |
| **Web & Research** | browseWeb, tavilySearch, perplexitySearch, tavilyAdvanced |
| **Media** | mediaTools, openaiImage |
| **System** | macosControl, think, templates |
| **Data** | analyzeData, notebookEdit |
| **Management** | manageTask, askOracle, sessionSummary |
| **Automation** | workflowAutomation, quickUpdate |

### Planning System

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/planning/plan-extract.ts` | Extract plan from natural language |
| `src/runtime/planning/plan-execute.ts` | Execute plan step-by-step with validation |

### Scheduling System

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/scheduling/scheduler.ts` | RRULE-based task scheduling |
| `src/runtime/scheduling/task-runner.ts` | Execute scheduled tasks |

### Autonomy System

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/autonomy/autonomy-loop.ts` | Long-running autonomous agent loop |
| `src/runtime/autonomy/oracle.ts` | Oracle escalation for critical decisions |
| `src/runtime/autonomy/stall-detect.ts` | Detect when agent is stalled |

### Hooks System

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/hooks/plan-validation.ts` | Validate plans before execution |
| `src/runtime/hooks/todo-check.ts` | Enforce todo completion before finishing |
| `src/runtime/hooks/skill-restrict.ts` | Validate skill usage permissions |

### Session Management

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/runtime/session/session-store.ts` | Session storage and retrieval |
| `src/runtime/session/session-history.ts` | Conversation history management |

### Web Interfaces

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/web/server.ts` | Combined WebSocket + HTTP server |
| `src/web/client/` | Original React web client |
| `src/web/fieldview/` | FieldView Classic terminal UI |

### Shared Components

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `src/types/shared-types.ts` | Shared TypeScript interfaces |
| `src/types/tool-types.ts` | Tool-specific type definitions |
| `src/shared/utils.ts` | Utility functions |
| `src/shared/constants.ts` | Application constants |
| `src/acp/acp.ts` | Anthropic Claude Protocol support |

### Configuration Files

| File | Responsibility |
|------|----------------|
| `packet/default_config.json` | Embedded default configuration |
| `packet/tool_schemas.openai.json` | OpenAI-format tool schemas |
| `tsconfig.json` | TypeScript compiler configuration |

